Heat butter and marshmallows in a large microwavable bowl on High for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir until smooth. Stir in cereal until well coated. Gently fold in candies. Cool 5 minutes. Measure cereal mixture in 1/2-cup portions. Using buttered hands, shape into loosely packed 3- to 4-inch balls. Wrap in plastic wrap and tie with ribbon or raffia.